    {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "id": "intro-text",
        "content": "Building modern web applications has never been more exciting — or more complex. In this guide, we'll walk through the key principles, tools, and patterns that separate good web apps from great ones.\n\nWhether you're just starting out or looking to level up your skills, this guide has something for everyone. We'll cover architecture decisions, performance optimization, accessibility, and much more.",
