    {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "id": "section-1-text",
        "content": "The best web applications share a set of core principles: they're fast, accessible, secure, and maintainable. Let's explore each of these in depth.\n\nPerformance isn't just a nice-to-have — it directly impacts user retention and conversion rates. Studies show that a 1-second delay in page load can reduce conversions by 7%. This means performance must be built in from the start, not bolted on at the end.",
        "align": "left",
        "color": "#374151",
        "fontSize": "1rem"
      }
